   "source": [
    "# Removing the outlairs \n",
    "Q1 = df.bmi.quantile(0.25)\n",
    "Q3 = df.bmi.quantile(0.75)\n",
    "\n",
    "IQR = Q3 - Q1\n",
    "\n",
    "lower_bond = Q1 - 1.5 * IQR\n",
    "upper_bond = Q3 + 1.5 * IQR\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f'Lower Bond : {lower_bond} \\n Upper Bond : {upper_bond}')\n"
   ]
  },

   "cell_type": "code",

   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "df_clean = df[(df.bmi >= lower_bond) & (df.bmi <= upper_bond)] # Removed Outlairs "
   ]
